hadiths[23]{hadithnumber,text}:
2927,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam thehar-thehar kar padhtey they, aap : (الحمد لله رب العالمين) padhtey , phir ruk jatey , phir « الرحمن الرحيم » padhtey phir ruk jatey , aur « ملك يوم الدين » padhtey they padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, 2- abu Ubaid bhi yehi padhtey they aur usi ko pasand kartey they padhi. , 3- Yahya bin Saeed umwi aur unkey siwa doosrey logon ney ibne-Jurej sey aur ibne-Jurej ney ibne-Abi Muleka key wastey sey Umme-Salma sey isi tarah riwayat ki hai, is hadees ki sanad muttasil nahin hai, kyonkey Les bin Saad ney ye hadees ibne-Abi Muleka sey ibne-Abi Muleka ney Yala bin Mamlak sey unhoney Umme-Salma (Raziallahu Anha) sey riwayat ki hai ke unhoney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki qirat ki keyfiyat eik eik harf alag kar key bayan ki. Les ki hadees ziyada sahih hai aur Les ki hadees mein ye zikr nahin hai ke aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam « ملك يوم الدين » '' padhtey they."
2928,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam , abu-Bakar o umr Raziallahu anhuma ( Raavi Zohri kehtey hain ke) aur mera khayal hai ke Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ney Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ka bhi naam liya ke ye sab log « ملك يوم الدين » padhtey they . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, 2- hum isey sirf Zohri ki riwayat sey jisey wo Anas bin Malik sey riwayat kartey hain sirf us Shekh yani Ayub bin Suwed Ramli ki riwayat sey hi jantey hain, 3- Zohri key baaz as-haab ( talaamiza ( ney ye hadees Zohri sey) mursalan ( riwayat ki hai ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam aur abu-Bakar o umr « ملك يوم الدين » padhtey they. aur abdur-Razzaaq ney Maamar sey , Maamar ney Zohri sey aur Zohri ney Saeed bin Musaiyab sey) mursalan ( riwayat ki hai ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam aur abu-Bakar o umr Raziallahu anhuma « ملك يوم الدين » padhtey they, ( yani is ko marfooan sirf Ayub bin Suwed hi ney riwayat kya hai, aur wo zaeef hain ( ."
2929,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney padha : « أن النفس بالنفس والعين بالعين  « بالعين  . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, 2- abu-Ali bin Yazeed , Yunus bin Yazeed key bhai hain, 3- Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari kehtey hain : is hadees ko Yunus bin Yazeed sey riwayat karney mein ibne-Mubarak munfarid ( tanha ( hain, 4- aur abu Ubaid ( Qasim bin Salam ( ney is hadees ki ittiba mein is tarah ( « العين  « بالعين » ( padha hai."
2930,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney padha « هل تستطيع ربك  . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, hum isey sirf Rushdain ki hadees sey jantey hain, 2- aur iski sanad qawi nahin hai, Rushdain bin Saad aur (Abdur-Rehman bin Ziyad bin Anam) Afriqi dono hadees bayan karney mein zaeef hain."
2931,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam padhtey they (إنه عمل غير صالح). Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- isi tarah kaee eik riwayaton ney Sabit Bunani sey is hadees ki riwayat ki hai. 2- ye hadees Shehar bin Hoshab sey Asma binte Yazeed key wastey sey bhi riwayat ki gaee hai. 3- mainey Abd bin Humed ko kehtey huye suna hai ke Asma binte Yazeed hi Umme-Salma Ansaariya hain, 4- ye dono hi hadisein merey nazdik eik hain. 5- Shehar bin Hoshab ney kaee hadisein Umme-Salma Ansaariya sey riwayat ki hain, aur Umme-Salma Ansaariya yehi Asma binte Yazeed hain. 6- Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai unhoney bhi Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey isi tarah riwayat ki hai."
2932,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney ye aayat is tarah padhi : (إنه عمل غير صالح).
2933,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney padha : (قد بلغت من لدني عذرا) yani (لدني) ko noon bhaari key sath padha. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, hum isey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain. 2- Umayya bin Khalid Suqa (bharosemand) hain. 3- اAbul Jaariya Abdi majhool (anjaan) Shekh hain, hum in ka naam nahin jantey."
2934,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney « في عين حمئة » padha. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, hum isey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain. 2- sahih ibne-Abbas ki qirat hai jo un sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai. 2- marvi (riwayat hui) hai ke ibne-Abbas aur Amr bin al-Aas (Raziallauh anhum) dono ney is aayat ki qirat mein aapas mein ikhtilaf kiya, aur apna maamla (faisle key liye) Kaab Ahbaar key paas ley gaey. agar unkey paas is barey mein Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey koi riwayat hoti to wo riwayat unkey liye kafi hoti , aur Kaab Ahbaar ki taraf unhen ruju ki hajat na rehti."
2935,"jange Badr key moqe par Romi (ehale kitab Nasara) ehale Faras (aatish parast majusiyon) par ghalib aagey. to ye chiz musalmanon ko badi pasand aai aur isi moqe par (الم غلبت الروم) se (يفرح المؤمنون) tak ki aayaat nazil huin. chunanche musalman ehale Rome key ehale Faras par ghalbe sey khush huye. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan gharib hai. 2- « غَلَبَتْ » aur « غُلِبَتْ » dono padha jata hai. kehtey hain : ehale Rome pehley maghloob huye phir ghalib aagey, aisey hi Nasar bin Ali ney «غَلَبَتْ» padha hai."
2936,unhoney Nabi Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key samney « خَلَقَكُمْ مِنْ ضَعْفٍ » ( zaad ke zabar ke sath) padha to aap ney farmaya : « مِنْ ضَعْفٍ » nahin « مِنْ ضُعْفٍ  (zaad pesh key sath) padho.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- hum isey sirf Fuzel bin Marzooq ki riwayat sey jantey hain.
2937,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam (فهل من مدكر) padhtey they . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
2938,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam « فروح وريحان وجنة نعيم  padhtey they . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, 2- usey hum sirf Harun Aawar ki riwayat sey hi jantey hain."
2939,"hum Sham pahunchey to Abu Darda (Raziallahu anhu) hamarey paas aaye aur kaha : kya tum mein koi shakhs aisa hai jo Abdullah bin Masood ki qirat ki tarah par qirat karta ho? to logon ney meri taraf ishara kiya, mainey kaha : haan , unhoney kaha : tum ney ye aayat « والليل إذا يغشى » Abdullah bin Masood ko kaisey padhtey huye suna hai? mainey kaha : mainey unhen « والليل إذا يغشى والذكر والأنثى  padhtey huye suna hai. Abu-Darda ney kaha : aur main , qism Allah ki, mainey bhi Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko aisa hi padhtey huye suna hai, aur ye log chahtey hain ke main isey (وما خلق) padhun (yani «وما خلق والذكر والأنثى») to main un ki baat na manunga. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Abdullah bin Masood ki qirat bhi isi tarah hai : « والليل إذا يغشى والنهار إذا تجلى والذكر والأنثى »."
2940,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney mujhey « إني أنا الرزاق ذو القوة المتين » padhaya hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
2941,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney padha : « وترى الناس سكارى وما هم بسكارى ». Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai. 2- Qatada Sahaba mein sey Anas Abu-Tufail key ilawa kisi aur Sahaba sey hum samaa (sun'na), nahin jantey. 3- ye riwayat merey nazdik mukhtasar hai. puri riwayat is tarah hai : riwayat ki gaee Qatada sey , Qatada ney riwayat ki Hasan Basri sey, aur Hasan Basri ney riwayat ki Imran bin Husain sey, hum Nabi Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath safar mein they to aap ney aayat « يا أيها الناس اتقوا ربكم  padhi , ( aagey ( puri hadees bayan ki. 4- Hakam bin Abdul-Malik ki hadees merey nazdik is hadees sey mukhtasar hai."
2942,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''un mein sey ya tum mein sey kisi key liye ye kehna bura hai ke main falan falan aayat bhool gaya, balke ye kaho ke wo bhula diya gaya padhi. tum Quran yad kartey dohraate raho, qism hai us zaat ki jis key qabzae qudrat mein meri jaan hai ! Quran logon key seenon sey nikal bhagney mein chopayon key apni rassi sey nikal bhagney ki bih nisbat ziyada tez hai.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2943,"un dono ney umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ko kehtey huye suna hai : main Hisham bin Hakim bin Hizaam key paas sey guzraa, wo Sura الفرقان padh rahey they. us waqt Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam zinda they, mainey un ki qirat suni , wo aisey harfon par padh rahey they, jin par Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney mujhey padhaya hi na tha. qarib tha ke main un par hamla kar deta magar mainey unhen (namaz padh leney tak ki) mohlat di. junhi unhoney salam pheraa mainey in ko unhen ki chadar unkey galey mein dal kar ghasita, mainey un sey puchha : ye Sura jisey mainey tumhen abhi padhtey huye suna hai, tumhen kis ney padhaai hai? kaha : mujhey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney padhaai hai. mainey kaha : tum ghalat kehtey ho, qism Allah ki ! Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney hi mujhey ye Sura padhaai jo tum padh rahey they padhi. , main unhen kheenchtaa huwa Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas ley gaya. mainey kaha : Allah key Rasool ! mainey inhen Sura الفرقان aisey harfon ( tariqon ( par padhtey huye suna hai jin par aap ney mujhey padhna nahin sikhaya hai jabke aap hi ney mujhey Sura الفرقان padhaya hai. phir aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Umar ! inhen chhod do, Hisham ! tum padho.'' to unhoney wohi qirat ki jo mainey un sey suni thi . aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''haan, aisi hi nazil hui hai.'' phir mujh sey aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Umar ! tum padho'' ,to mainey isi tarah padha jis tarah aap ney mujhey padhaya tha, aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''haan, isi tarah nazil ki gaee hai.''  phir aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''ye Quran saat harfon par utara gaya hai, to jo qirat tumhen aasan lagey usi qirat par tum Quran padho.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Malik bin Anas ney Zohri sey isi sanad key sath isi tarah riwayat ki hai, lekin unhoney apni riwayat mein Miswar bin Makhrima ka zikr nahin kiya."
2944,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam Jibreel (Alaihissalam) sey miley . aap ney farmaya : ''Jibreel ! main eik ummi (un padh) qom key paas Nabi bana kar bheja gaya hun, un mein boodhi aurten aur boodhey mard hain, ladkey aur ladkiyan hain, un mein aisey log bhi hain jinhoney kabhi koi kitab padhi hi nahin hai to Jibreel (Alaihissalam) ney kaha : Muhammad ! Quran saat harfon par nazil huwa hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein umr , Huzefa bin Yamaan , Abu-Hurera , aur Umme Ayub (Raziallauh anhum) Umme Ayub ( abu-Ayyub Ansari ki biwi ( . aur Samura , ibne-Abbas, Abu Jaheem bin Haris bin Simma, Amr bin al-Aas aur Abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi ahadees aai hain. 3- Ubai-bin Kaab sey ye hadees mutaaddid (bahut si) sanadon sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai."
2945,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jisney apney bhai ki koi duniyaawi musibat door ki to Allah Taala uski qiyamat key din koi na koi musibat door farmaeyga. aur jisney kisi musalman ki parda poshi ki. to Allah uski duniya aur aakhirat mein parda poshi kerega, aur jisney kisi tang dast key sath aasani ki, to Allah Taala duniya aur aakhirat mein uskey liye aasani paida farmaeyga. Allah apney bandey ki madad mein hota hai jab tak banda apney bhai ki madad karta rehta hai, aur jo aisi raah chalta hai jis mein usey ilm ki talash hoti hai to Allah Taala uskey liye jannat ka raasta humwaar kar deta hai aur jab qom ( log ( masjid mein beth kar Kalamullah (Quran) ki tilawat kartey hain aur isey padhtey padhaatey (samajhtey samjhaatey) hain to un par sakeenat nazil hoti hai, unhen rehmate Ilaahi dhanp leti hai. malaaika unhen apney gherey mein liye rehtey hain, jis key amal ney isey peechhey kar diya to aakhirat mein uska nasab usey aagey nahin badha sakta.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- aisey hi kaee riwayaton ney isi hadees ki tarah Aamash sey Aamash ney abu-Saaleh key wastey sey , aur abu-Saaleh ney Abu-Hurera key wastey sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki hai. 2- Asbaat bin Muhammad ney bhi Aamash sey riwayat ki hai, (is riwayat mein hai ke) Aamash kehtey hain : mujh sey bayan kiya gaya hai Abu-Saaleh key wastey sey aur Abu-Saaleh ney Abu-Hurera key wastey sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat kartey hain phir is hadees ka baaz hissa zikr kiya."
2946,"mainey kaha : Allah key Rasool ! main kitney dino mein Quran padh dalun? aap ney farmaya : ''mahiney main eik baar khatam karo'' ,mainey kaha main is sey badh kar) yani kam muddat mein) khatam karney ki taqat rakhta hun. aap ney farmaya : ''to bees din mein khatam karo.'' mainey kaha : main is sey ziyada ki yani aur bhi kam muddat mein khatam karney ki taqat rakhta hun. aap ney farmaya : ''pandarah din mein khatam kar liya karo.'' mainey kaha : main is sey bhi ziyada ki taqat rakhta hun. aap ney farmaya : ''das din mein khatam kar liya karo.'' mainey kaha : main is sey bhi ziyada ki taqat rakhta hun, aap ney farmaya : ''paanch din mein khatam kar liya karo.'' mainey kaha : main is sey bhi ziyada ki taqat rakhta hun. to aap ney mujhey paanch din sey kam muddat mein Quran khatam karney ki ijazat nahin di. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan sahih gharib hai. 2- ye hadees ba-tareeq : (أبي بردة an عبد الله بن عمرو) gharib samjhi gaee hai. 3- ye hadees kaee sanadon sey Abdullah bin Amr sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai. Abdullah bin Amr sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jisney Quran teen din sey kam muddat mein padha, usney Quran ko nahin samjha.'' 4- Abdullah bin Amr sey) ye bhi) marvi (riwayat hui) hai ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney un sey farmaya : ''Quran chaalis din mein padh dala karo.''  5- Is-haq bin Ibrahim bin Raahviya kehtey hain : hum is hadees ki bina par kisi aadmi key liye ye pasand nahin kartey ke is par chaalis din sey ziyada guzar jaeyn aur wo Quran pak khatam na kar chuka ho. 6- is hadees ki bina par jo Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai baaz ehle-ilm kehtey hain ke teen din sey kam muddat mein Quran padh kar na khatam kiya jaey. 7- aur baaz ehle-ilm ney iski rukhsat (chhoot) di hai. 8- aur Usman bin Affaan sey mutalliq hai marvi (riwayat hui) hai ke wo witr ki eik rakat mein pura Quran padh daltey they. 9- Saeed bin Juber sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai ke unhoney Kaba key andar eik rakat mein pura Quran padha. 10- qirat mein thehar thehar kar padhna ehle-ilm key nazdik pasandida hai."
2947,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney un sey farmaya : ''chaalis din mein Quran pura padh liya karo.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- ba'zon ney Maamar sey, aur Maamar ney Simaak bin Fazal key wastey sey Wahab bin Munabbah sey riwayat ki hai, ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Abdullah bin Amr Raziallahu anhuma ko hukm diya ke wo Quran chaalis din mein padha karen."
2948,"eik shakhs ney arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! kon sa amal Allah ko ziyada pasand hai? aap ney farmaya : «الحال» aur «المرتحل» (utarney aur kooch karney wala) amal. usney kaha : «الحال» aur «المرتحل» (utarney aur kooch karney wala) sey kya murad hai? aap ney farmaya : ''jo Quran shuru sey ley kar aakhir tak padhta hai, jab bhi wo utarta hai kooch kar deta hai.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai. 2- hum isey sirf ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ki is riwayat sey jantey hain jo is sanad sey aai hai aur iski sanad ziyada qawi nahin hai."
2949,Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''us ney Quran samjha hi nahin jisney teen din sey kam muddat mein Quran khatam kar dala.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
